<item>
            <title>[LU-19067] sanity-quota: check_system_is_clean() failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19067</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for jianyu &amp;lt;yujian@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/fbfb6af2-1002-4c5f-af12-acb2dd4115c9&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/fbfb6af2-1002-4c5f-af12-acb2dd4115c9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/106&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/106&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-570.17.1.el9_6.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/106&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/106&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.53.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In full-dne-zfs-part-2 test session, after running parallel-scale-nfsv3, check_system_is_clean() failed at the beginning of sanity-quota, which caused the test suite to exit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test output showed &quot;Files for group (quota_usr):&quot;, but the real error should be &quot;Used space(208) for group quota_usr isn&apos;t 0.&quot;, which was not displayed in the test output.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
